CBRE and Oxford Commercial are excited to be exclusively offering for lease this recently refurbed, standalone creative opportunity in the dynamic Central Park precinct of Chippendale.

Key Features of 63 Kensington Street:

• 383sqm* of Lettable Area, to be taken as either one floor (170sqm*) or whole building
• Open plan configuration
• Exposed brick interior
• High timber ceilings and exposed services throughout
• Exclusive outdoor areas and terraces
• Could suit a multitude of uses, from a Corporate HQ to Student Accommodation (STCA)
• 1 secure car park

Key Locational Benefits:
• Train Station – 5 min walk to both train station and light rail
• Bus – 55 bus routes operate from Central Station
• Foot – 1.5km from Town Hall Train Station, 850m to
• Redfern Train Station and 850m from Central Station
• Car – Central park has the largest car share hub in Australia
• Surrounded by award winning amenity such as Spice Alley and Broadway
• In close proximity to UTS, University of Sydney and Notre Dame University

For further information please contact the exclusive agents.

*Approx.
